channel.title: Ssi2?
channel.description:
Guys, every script I use I keep getting this message when I try to run/compile the script. [code]Include file C:\Documents and Settings\Matthew\My Documents\Matt\Media Player\Green Day\Autofighter Cheat Package\Macros\SCAR 3.15\includes\ssi2.txt does not exist. Failed when compiling[/code]
Don't worry about everything before the SCAR 3.15 file...I just put it there to hide it from my mom...along with the rest of my macros and such.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 07, 2008, 01:33:10 pm[/size][hr]Thanks to the all includes.zip I just downloaded, that's no longer a problem...the problem now is this: [code]Line 54: [Error] (68:51): Duplicate identifier 'UpChars' in script C:\Documents and Settings\Matthew\My Documents\Matt\Media Player\Green Day\Autofighter Cheat Package\Macros\SCAR 3.15\includes\ssi2.txt[/code] Same file...maybe my computer just doesn't like ssi2.txt

item.title: Ssi2?
item.dc:creator: @Surajd Surajd
item.description:
@Surajd wrote:

Is the SRL include the latest?

EDIT: Read the sticky by IP-Drowner:
"Is there something wrong with your script? Something as an Include file? Then GET A NEW SCRIPT, since they must be out-dated then. Best place to look for much more better and advanced scripts is the SRL-Forums, however, you must be registered there for 7 days and have posted 10 useful posts Wink So don’t go spamming!

Most of the scripts around here are OUT-DATED, so don’t bother posting if the first posts date (inc. Edit date) is more than ONE MONTH old!

The best include to get is SRL! Since it is the ONLY include updated for the NEW RuneScape."

So yeah, you probably need the latest SRL include.
